{
  "stem": "1208.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "And you know, the fantasies I had of what happened to him, how did he die.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "And I was still in school in Berlin.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "And a month later, or perhaps a little less, my mother wrote another letter saying she had gotten a deportation notice saying that she was being relocated to the east, that my brothers had gotten the same notice in Cologne.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "And they were to leave on May 8, 1942 to somewhere in the east.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I remember that day very well at school.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was raining very hard.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And after I read the letter, I stormed out of the room.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I had to sort out my feelings.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What was I going to do?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I came back to the room.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I sat down and wrote a letter to the Gestapo saying, I'm Karoline Wolff's daughter, Hannelore, and I wish to go with her to be relocated in the east.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "My roommates thought I was out of my mind and said, why can't you wait until tomorrow?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You'll think about it differently.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "To me, there was only one way.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So I sent the letter off.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And a few weeks later, I got an official letter from the Gestapo saying that they allowed me to travel from Berlin to Weimar to be transported.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "One needed a document to be on the train.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So I immediately set to work and packed a few things, mainly my books, my beloved books.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I rode the train, on the train to Weimar to be with my mother.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And on May 8, 1942, my mother's birthday, we walked to the [NON-ENGLISH], which is an animal hall.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This is where they assembled us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Why they picked an animal hall is anybody's guess.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was very humiliating.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
